genresAdvancedInfo.name: guitar case
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Guitar case is a genre of music that is characterized by its focus on acoustic guitar arrangements. It typically features solo guitar performances or small ensembles that showcase the versatility and beauty of the instrument. This genre often draws from a variety of musical traditions, including folk, blues, and classical, and can range from gentle and contemplative to lively and upbeat.
